BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Moon enters Cancer
DESCRIPTION:Moon enters Cancer \n- Moon in Cancer 0°00’ \n \nYour feeling of safety is now related to your home, family and related activities such as cooking and gardening.  \n \nYou may be prone to emotional fluctuations; you should learn to forgive and forget in order to avoid depression from thinking too much about things. Your perception of the world can be very subjective; try to create a certain distance without being bitter. Due to your rich emotional manifestation you can create a real sense of belonging in the world. \n \nOrgans influenced by Cancer sign:  \nStomach, mucosa, ovary, womb, breast, pleura, peritoneum, lymph system, breastbone \n \nMoon calendar:  \nhttps://mooncalendar.astro-seek.com
DTSTART:20270120T092000Z
DTEND:20270120T092000Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T174007Z
UID:78_moon_enters_cancer
END:VEVENT
